<div style="font-family:serif;">
:<font size="15">פּעם</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
פּעמה  -  פּעם / pa‛am  pa‛ămâh / pah'-am, pah-am-aw'

===Etymology===
From {{HH|6470}}; 

===Noun===
'''פּעם'''

# a [[stroke]], literally or figuratively (in various applications): - anvil, corner, foot (-step), going, [hundred-] fold, X now, (this) + once, order, rank, step, + thrice, [often-], second, this, two) time (-s), twice, wheel.

